national men's 45-and-older hardcourt championships at the Westlake Tennis & 
Swim Club. 
</P>
<P>
 The National Foundation of Wheelchair Tennis will sponsor a tournament, 
believed to be the first of its kind in the San Fernando Valley, Aug. 19-21 at 
the Balboa Tennis Center in Encino. The tournament will have multiple flights, 
age and gender divisions. 
