<P>
 All games will be played at Ventura College. 
</P>
<P>
 Information: (805) 653-6089. Football 
</P>
<P>
 Rick Hayashida, an assistant football coach at Chaminade High for the past 
three seasons, has been added to the staff at El Camino Real. 
</P>
