ORANGE COUNTY BRIEFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Pacific Scientific Co.: The company said Tuesday that it is restructuring its 
Rockford, Ill., operations by creating a new division in Charlestown, Mass. 
</P>
<P>
 The new motion technology division will develop control systems, software and 
systems integration. The move allows the Rockford plant to continue to serve 
the market for direct-current motors and generators. 
</P>
<P>
 The two divisions will continue to share marketing, sales and other joint 
functions through the end of the year. 
</P>
<P>
 Pacific Scientific, based in Newport Beach, is a maker of electrical and 
safety equipment. 
</P>
